dct_alternative_sm: Flemmings Kriegskarte Nr. 24 (Als nordwestliches Anschlußblatt dient Kriegskarte Nr. 23, Nördliche Westfront)
dct_description_sm: Coordinates are approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Relief shown by shading and spot heights.
Legend shows cities, villages, fortresses, forts, railroads and stations, various roads, canals, forests, marshland, boundaries.
Color legend shows French, Belgian, German, Luxembourg, and Swiss territory.
